Tom Barrack, Colony Capital’s CEO, spoke exclusively with CNBC’s Hadley Gamble in Abu Dhabi, UAE. The wide-ranging interview covers the race to 2020, Jared Kushner’s “deal of the century” and the likelihood of Lebanon solving its fiscal crisis.
